{"tid":956727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【究竟想Sell乜】TVB神秘廣告引網民爆料　15年後再現疑涉一男子","createTime":"2018-12-26T13:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T19:20:59.000Z","uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3363dba5d72bf787c70bddf48251ae71b90e26ab","tid":956727,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDb7qpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDb7qpg.jpg&h=1d51d3f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個聖誕夜在無綫電視翡翠台黃金時段播放的神秘廣告，在拆禮物日成為全城網民的焦點。這則僅約5秒的廣告除背景綻放的煙花外，只顯示一間公司名稱，令網民議論紛紛。有人爆料15年前TVB曾現類似廣告，又有人爆出該廣告出自一間公司，陰謀論處處，經查冊發現原來網民爆料並非無的放矢，所有線索都直指一名周姓男子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NmOUh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NmOUh3.jpg&h=01489c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聖誕夜突然出現的古怪廣告，吸引全城關注，引起網民熱烈討論。（網上片段截圖</span><br />\n<br />\nTVB昨晚黃金時段不止一次出現一個極為奇怪、看上去與時代脫節的神秘廣告，廣告以放煙花畫面襯底，正中央以黃色大字寫出「蘋果廣告製作公司」字樣。不少網民心生好奇，卻發現廣告除了公司名稱，沒再出現涉事公司任何資料，就算網民在Google搜尋，也未見有關公司的聯絡方法，令人生疑不為宣傳的廣告，背後究竟在打什麼主意。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民直指這廣告感覺很奇怪，稱第一眼看到還誤以為在看內地電視，有人腦洞大開想出不少陰謀論，覺得如非為宣傳，這5秒內容猶如向某特定目標或人士宣示一些暗語，有人則回憶起2003年時也曾見過極相似的廣告，更留言指：「2003年就係晚晚播呢個廣告，跟住SARS就嚟」，說法甚為恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gp6WiKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGp6WiKT.jpg&h=c1f68172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有網民從神秘廣告中聯想到SARS，指當年出現蘋果電影的煙花廣告後，香港就出現疫情。（資料圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n翻看被指2003年出現的廣告，涉事公司叫「蘋果電影」，惟畫面中一樣以煙花作背景，也是黃色大字寫上公司名，除公司名不同外，另一分別是今年新廣告以歌曲為背景音樂，當年卻有男聲說出旁白：「世界和平，萬眾歡騰，蘋果電影。」<br />\n<br />\n全城關注下更現網民爆料，有人貼出截圖，顯示有人大爆該廣告來自一間名為「周創發廣告公司」，又指該公司八十、九十年代興起，至1996年息微，爆料人指涉事的「蘋果」廣告，正是他為該公司老闆的弟弟「周志強」所製作，更估計今年突然再現，或因「周志強」想重出江湖。<br />\n<br />\n另有網民爆料，指有「前輩」提及「蘋果廣告製作公司」疑似係由周創發弟弟、廣告人周志強於1996年創立，指當年TVB曾見「周創發廣告雜誌」，主力賣珠寶廣告，又認出新廣告背景音樂是1992年劉德華歌曲《真我的風采》。<br />\n<br />\n就網民種種爆料，《香港01》深入查冊，發現果然有所關連，均指向同一名周姓男子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tjK1uRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtjK1uRP.jpg&h=23266736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聖誕夜突然出現的古怪廣告引起網民關注，有人指在2003年時TVB也曾出現極為相似的廣告，質疑當中大有關連。（網上片段截圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gfF8IU-2jnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgfF8IU-2jnY&d=pJzRYsdkl93uV2yzkgrKUWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=b4212a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gfF8IU-2jnY</a><br />\n<br />\n2003年及今年廣告中提及的「蘋果電影製作有限公司」和「蘋果廣告製作公司」，均由名為「周自強」的男子持有，其中「蘋果廣告製作公司」只有商業登記卻未有公司註冊紀錄，至於「蘋果電影製作有限公司」，則於2016年已告解散，按解散前的公司年報顯示，周自強當時身份為董事。<br />\n<br />\n至於被網民爆出「周創發廣告公司」，應該為「周創發有限公司」，據公司註冊處資料，該公司1993年成立但於2006年解散，據該公司1997年年報，周自強與周創發共同持有公司，股份比例為4比6。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVmrFYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVmrFYM.jpg&h=010275a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRgZ0YS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRgZ0YS.jpg&h=1e458328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmBLb5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmBLb5C.jpg&h=61815ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聖誕夜突然出現的古怪廣告引起網民關注，有人爆料指廣告負責人與早年曾在TVB大賣珠寶廣告的周創發有限公司有關。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNSZgxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNSZgxo.jpg&h=6b9c453f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnR3Jcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnR3Jcs.jpg&h=29c1fc5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30giLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30giLQ.jpg&h=0512db9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpbGuSy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpbGuSy.jpg&h=679a6135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫電視回覆《香港01》時，未多談這個廣告的接洽細節，只表示「本台播出的廣告均經有關部門審查，確保符合電視通用業務守則。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/275554/究竟想sell乜-tvb神秘廣告引網民爆料-15年後再現疑涉一男子\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F275554%2F%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%83%B3sell%E4%B9%9C-tvb%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E5%BC%95%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-15%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90&d=pJzRYsdkl93uV2yzkgrKUWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=34fcd431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/275554/究竟想sell乜-tvb神秘廣告引網民爆料-15年後再現疑涉一男子</a>"},{"pid":"a1d3195ffa65f5a43c200ad2788400c4079ea0b2","tid":956727,"uid":63202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"唔講仲以為沙士前得依個廣告播過 On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ded3c849b708990b872030a54bcf953d88bc80","tid":956727,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e196a1312af2d7626d8d9bb5bdfa50a5cef79267","tid":956727,"uid":182499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"班陰毛撚笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8392294de6a331362b9a3b649032e0cd3f1e509f","tid":956727,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/956641/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/956641/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1a5ca942a392f3769f607e8b09b31869322d5e","tid":956727,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"之前沙士，今次豬瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f98f2d9a343f83ac2a4c96325396c05e1a6cde8","tid":956727,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:57:41.000Z","msg":"無綫電視回覆《香港01》時，未多談這個廣告的接洽細節<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2edc5119a3f95fe4e66b72096cfc806a92d3fc3","tid":956727,"uid":120123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"數字電台（英語：Number Station），又稱暗號廣播，是一種不明發射來源的短波電台。此類電台通常持續播送數字、字母、脈衝聲調或者摩爾斯電碼，多數使用女性聲音，也有少量男性以及兒童聲音播送。英語、中文、俄語、西班牙文等多種語言的數字電台都有出現的記錄。<br />\n<br />\n一種普遍的觀點認為，此類電台被用於傳遞間諜信息，但是這種說法從來沒有被任何一個國家的政府所承認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話唔定類似呢d野呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b323a4541ae66ca1b6d0f4e17a9170b3329c247b","tid":956727,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06c18e43f360989692f32fa4c66089bd0cd1f88c","tid":956727,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b323a4541ae66ca1b6d0f4e17a9170b3329c247b","tid":956727,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f98f2d9a343f83ac2a4c96325396c05e1a6cde8","tid":956727,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:57:41.000Z","msg":"無綫電視回覆《香港01》時，未多談這個廣告的接洽細節<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"5秒廣告喎<br />\n咁短除非好有錢先會肯接呢單生意"},{"pid":"536c34fc072745da086d0f943fad2549b158486f","tid":956727,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"好似美國睇睇下電視有個帶面具嘅人出黎唔知做乜一樣"},{"pid":"6f9e47d8d9f5b8ded067a77766d66c09e5d712be","tid":956727,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去旅行呀?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100cf6ff4ef6db6e6bd284a3cd0b19548bb1b765","tid":956727,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T19:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}